Tickit-Widget-TTree

This is a widget for Tickit (currently http://search.cpan.org/~pevans/Tickit-0.04/)
that displays a browsable file tree. It is named after the old XTree app for
DOS, except it's for Tickit. Also, tea tree is good for you.

Currently it only displays the tree.

TODO

